  • Constructor Details

    • ParsedResume

      @Deprecated public ParsedResume()
      Deprecated.
      You should never create one of these. Instead, these are output by the Sovren Resume Parser. Sovren does not support manually-created resumes to be used in the AI Matching engine.

      Load a parsed resume from a json file using UTF-8 encoding. This is useful when you have stored parse results to disk for use later.
